WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:02.166
Linmer, this stupid woman

2
00:00:02.733 --> 00:00:04.000
Love me so much

3
00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:08.266
The Lin Group will be mine sooner or later

4
00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:09.900
Humph

5
00:00:14.900 --> 00:00:17.566
Tell me how I can leave my sister

6
00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:21.233
Let me tell you a story first

7
00:00:22.966 --> 00:00:24.233
20 years ago

8
00:00:24.500 --> 00:00:28.766
My father's place was bought by a rich man

9
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:31.100
They beat my father to death

10
00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:33.100
And insulted my mother

11
00:00:34.566 --> 00:00:36.433
It made me an orphan.

12
00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:39.233
Don't expect me to feel sorry for you.

13
00:00:43.466 --> 00:00:46.033
But then I realized something.

14
00:00:46.366 --> 00:00:47.433
I promise.

15
00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:50.966
I want to become a rich man

16
00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:53.033
Because of money

17
00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:56.833
You can take the lives of others at will.

18
00:00:58.700 --> 00:01:01.166
So you use the woman around you who loves you

19
00:01:01.466 --> 00:01:03.033
To achieve your despicable goals

20
00:01:04.266 --> 00:01:05.600
She has to love me

21
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:07.266
What can I do?

